    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, i've heard all that before. the \"it gets better\" talk, the \"reach out\" stuff... it doesn't change the math. the math is what matters, and the math says i don't exist anymore. my entire life's work was a ghost. how can anyone help me find meaning when the very foundation of my reality was a mistake? it feels like i'm just a glitch in a system that's already collapsed.",
